<H1><a name="membership">Membership Information</a></H1>

Membership includes:
<UL>
<LI>
Subscription to <!WA17><a href="#sigactnews"><cite>SIGACT News</cite></a>
<LI>
Subscription to <!WA18><a href="#online"><cite>SIGACT News Online</cite></a>
<LI>
Reduced-rate registration for
SIGACT sponsored <!WA19><a href="#conferences">conferences</a>
<LI>
Individually mailed Call for Papers and Conference Schedules for
SIGACT sponsored <!WA20><a href="#conferences">conferences</a>
</UL>

More information
is available on
<!WA21><a href=http://info.acm.org/catalog/sigs/sigact.html>how to
join SIGACT</a>.

